We still can't pass the ball out of defence. We lack creativity and ideas through the middle. We also desperately need another striker. I keep telling people that Greenwood cannot be relied upon because he need to improve on a lot of things, and Martial doesn't do enough.

I really hope I get to see Pogba and Fernandes play together. I also hope we bring in some new drill coaches, otherwise our team will continue to struggle no matter what players we bring in.
